<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="relation-n">relation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'leɪʃn/    美 /rɪ'leɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u-relationship">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 关系；联系 (relationship)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>relation between</strong> them is that of teacher and pupil. 
他们是师生关系。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[用复数] 交往；事务：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He established good <strong>relations with</strong> his neighbors.
他和邻居建立了良好的关系。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-relative">3.★ <strong>亲属；家属 (relative)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>distant relation</strong>
远亲</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-relation-to">in relation to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用语] 关于；与…相比：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have a lot to say in relation to this affair. 
关于这件事，我有很多话要说。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Women’s earnings are still low in relation to men’s.
女性的收入相对于男性而言还是偏低。</p></div></div>